code: const GOOGLE_API_KEY=process.env.REACT_APP_GOOGLE_API_KEY;const GOOGLE_CX=process.env.REACT_APP_GOOGLE_CX;export async function searchGoogle(query){if(!GOOGLE_API_KEY||!GOOGLE_CX){throw new Error("Missing Google API key or CX");}const url=`https://www.googleapis.com/customsearch/v1?q=${encodeURIComponent(query)}&key=${GOOGLE_API_KEY}&cx=${GOOGLE_CX}`;console.log("Request URL:",url);const response=await fetch(url);if(!response.ok){throw new Error("Failed to fetch search results");}const data=await response.json();console.log("Google API full response:",data);return data.items||[];}
